o args_env
  use of command line arguments and environment variables

o conf_ini
  Parse a minimal ini file. Lookup for a specific section and parse its
  properties split in categories.

o dir_parse
  parsing members of a directory and recurse

o epoll
  use of epoll with signalfd

o glob
  use glob pattern matching on strings

o input
  o evdev
    deal with evdev input devices

o insmod
  load and init a kernel module

o network_server
  o pre-fork_socket_unix_tcp
    a TCP/IPv4 network server with pre-fork for connexion processing. Connexion
    sockets are passed using unix sockets.

o so
  compile a shared lib

o thread
  create a thread

o uevents_monitor
  monitor uevents from the kernel
